en_129941_0	Deputy Minister of Foreign Affairs Harsha De Silva says that the statement made by former President Mahinda Rajapaksa that the present government has obtained loans amounting to USD 6.361 billion was incorrect.
en_129941_1	He stated this at a media briefing in Colombo today.
en_129941_2	The Deputy Minister also requested not to hinder the efforts taken by the government to repay the loans taken by the previous government.
